These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, pall-mall, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
2. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
3. the swisher-smoker is not to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##8
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | swisher | vegafina | game |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, snake, bird
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
2. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | snake | ferret | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, action, comedy
1. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy | family | action |

