.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, goat, bird
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | bird | goat | frog |

