3. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |       3       |    4     |
| Color   | amber | apricot | purple | red |

